honestly i can't explain how amazing i feel inside watching you give back all of thjs food! it makes me so incredibly happy that the very fortunate are donating to the less fortunate like myself! i'm a regular user of the food bank in my local area! i use the food bank at least once a month to help with nappies,food,toiletries etc! me and my family don't get much money but when we do get paid we ALWAYS add a few extra things in to give to the food bank!

it makes my heart so happy that food banks exist because honestly i couldn't survive on £350 a month to feed my son,myself,my pets & my partner! we virtually live on the poverty line but i will ALWAYS give back to whatever i can! even if it's just a 20p pack of instant mash potato or a pack of nappies,nobody knows how much that truly helps families like mine!❤️
